msgid "**To draw a rectangle or an ellipse:**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/drawing_animation_levels.rst:427
msgid ""
"Click to define the upper left corner, drag, and release to define the "
"bottom right corner. If you press the Shift key while dragging, the shape"
" will be regular, i.e. a square or a circle; if you press the Alt key, "
"shapes will be drawn starting from their center."
