"selection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/drawing_animation_levels.rst:769
msgid ""
"Thickness sets the thickness of the selected vectors. In case the "
"selected vectors have a variable thickness, or different thickness "
"values, the highest value is displayed, and any change will affect the "
"other values accordingly. This is available for Vector drawings "
"only."
