"will include them as well, preserving them and their original layering "
"position in case the group is released."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/drawing_animation_levels.rst:955
msgid ""
"It is not possible to define a group if the selection includes only some "
"strokes belonging to a group."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/drawing_animation_levels.rst:957
msgid ""
"When a group is released, if no other group is defined in the same "
"drawing, all the vectors will lie on the same layer; if other groups are "
"defined, the vectors of the released group will lie on a layer placed "
"behind, in front of, or between the other groups, according to the "
"original group layering position."
