#: ../../source/drawing_animation_levels.rst:959
msgid ""
"It is possible to enter groups to isolate them visually from the rest of "
"the drawing and better understand which vectors are inside and which "
"outside the group. In this way it is also easier to work on the drawing, "
"for instance to fill an area or to change the color of some vectors."
